menu "Aliro reader"

    config WOZ_ALIRO_LAB
        bool "Aliro Lab transaction trace"
        default n
        help
            Emit structured "[ALAB] t=<us> ev=..." lines at transaction phase
            boundaries (connect, auth, ranging setup, first range, bolt) so
            tools/aliro_lab.py can turn a captured serial log into a scored
            walk-up report. Diagnostics only: default off, and every trace
            call compiles out of the firmware when disabled.

endmenu
